<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:12:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>数据显示，苹果 4 月份 iPhone 在中国销量猛增 52%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-sales-april-jump-52-data-shows-2024-05-28/</link><description>路透社根据周二的行业数据计算得出，苹果 4 月份在中国的 iPhone 销量同比增长 52%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 08:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-sales-april-jump-52-data-shows-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>新冠疫情过后，中国重返非洲并加大矿产资源投入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/post-covid-china-is-back-africa-doubling-down-minerals-2024-05-28/</link><description>路透社对贷款、投资和贸易数据的分析显示，中国的旗舰经济合作计划在全球大流行期间的平静期后正在反弹，其中非洲是主要焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 06:05:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/post-covid-china-is-back-africa-doubling-down-minerals-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁停止红海袭击民用船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-red-sea-attacks-civilian-ships-end-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，中国外交部长王毅在北京会见也门外长时，中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，并确保红海航行安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-red-sea-attacks-civilian-ships-end-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统感谢紧急升空对抗中国演习的飞行员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-thanks-pilots-who-scrambled-against-china-drills-2024-05-28/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周二在听取有关前线空军基地事件的通报时，对上周在台湾绕岛军演期间与中国进行紧急升空的战斗机飞行员表示感谢。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-thanks-pilots-who-scrambled-against-china-drills-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美同意通过持续对话管控海上风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-agree-manage-maritime-risks-through-continued-dialogue-2024-05-28/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，中美就海洋事务举行磋商，双方同意保持对话、管控风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 04:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-agree-manage-maritime-risks-through-continued-dialogue-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳斥手机入境检查的说法“荒谬”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-preposterous-claims-entry-checks-phones-2024-05-28/</link><description>当局周二表示，有关从 7 月 1 日起所有抵达中国的人都将接受手机检查的说法是错误的，并称其为“反华势力”歪曲事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 04:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-preposterous-claims-entry-checks-phones-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰银行将以 7.3 亿美元收购德国银行 Hauck Aufhäuser Lamp</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</link><description>荷兰银行已同意以 6.72 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）收购私人银行 Hauck Aufhäuser Lampe (HAL)，巩固其作为德国三大财富管理公司之一的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 03:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行言论提振风险偏好，亚洲股市小幅走高，美元走软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</link><description>亚洲股市周二小幅走高，而美元连续第三个交易日处于弱势，因欧洲即将降息的预期加剧，刺激了风险偏好。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、美国、日本核特使谴责朝鲜发射卫星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-japan-nuclear-envoys-condemn-north-korea-satellite-launch-2024-05-28/</link><description>首尔外交部表示，韩国、美国和日本的核特使在周二的电话中强烈谴责朝鲜最近发射卫星的企图。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:20:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-japan-nuclear-envoys-condemn-north-korea-satellite-launch-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>数据公布前美元小幅下跌，预计 2024 年首次月度下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-ebbs-markets-await-key-global-inflation-reports-2024-05-28/</link><description>美元周二小幅下跌，但兑其他货币仍处于窄幅区间，主要经济体本周将公布关键通胀数据，这些数据可能为全球利率前景提供信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 00:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-ebbs-markets-await-key-global-inflation-reports-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，诺基亚将向葡萄牙 MEO 供应 5G 无线电设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-supply-5g-radio-equipment-portugals-meo-sources-say-2024-05-27/</link><description>据诺基亚内部博客文章和两位知情人士透露，诺基亚将赢得一份向葡萄牙电信运营商 MEO 供应 5G 无线电设备的合同。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-supply-5g-radio-equipment-portugals-meo-sources-say-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟通过法律增加国内绿色技术产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/eu-clears-law-increase-domestic-green-tech-production-2024-05-27/</link><description>欧盟各国政府周一正式通过了一项新法律，旨在确保欧盟生产 40% 的太阳能电池板、风力涡轮机、热泵和其他清洁技术设备，并帮助欧洲工业与美国和中国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/eu-clears-law-increase-domestic-green-tech-production-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本警告居民躲避朝鲜导弹威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-residents-take-cover-north-korean-missile-threat-2024-05-27/</link><description>日本政府周一向南部居民发出紧急警告，要求他们躲避朝鲜导弹的可能威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-residents-take-cover-north-korean-missile-threat-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>据《环球时报》报道，中国工业界寻求对欧盟猪肉进口进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-industry-seek-probe-into-eu-pork-imports-global-times-reports-2024-05-27/</link><description>官方支持的《环球时报》周六援引一位未透露姓名的“业内人士”的话说，中国企业计划要求当局对从欧盟进口的部分猪肉产品展开反倾销调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-industry-seek-probe-into-eu-pork-imports-global-times-reports-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔全球表示，中国的房地产刺激措施增加了中小城市银行的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-stimulus-raises-risks-banks-smaller-cities-sp-global-says-2024-05-27/</link><description>标准普尔全球周一表示，中国为重振陷入困境的房地产市场而采取的最新举措可能会给在低线城市运营的银行带来风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-stimulus-raises-risks-banks-smaller-cities-sp-global-says-2024-05-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>